# | to bind multiple similar programs use additional modifier. Ex: 
# | 	- VSCode Hyper+C & PHPStorm Hyper+Shift+C
# | 	- Dbeaver Hyper+D & MySqlWorkbench Hyper+Shift+D
# | 
# | where is executable file of program: which <package>
# | 
# | FREE KEYS: [?]
# | 
